i am waiting for that he said refusing to elaborate 
the truce is expected to be disregarded but the tokyo talks are 
still regarded as a steppingstone to the possibility of political 
progress to end the war 
the phnom penh government hopes the talks also will cover an end 
to arms supplies to the guerrilla factions formation of a national 
