korea was partitioned at the 38th parallel after world war ii in 
1950 the soviet union backed the communist north koreans 
threeyear invasion of ussupported south korea that bitter war 
turned the south into one of the united states staunchest allies 
but koreans have always dreamed of reunification 
the talks are the fruit of seouls bid to woo the rapidly 
reforming warsaw pact countries aiming both to open new markets and 
