stifled dissent on the first anniversary of the bloody demise of 
chinas democracy movement 
all gates to beijing university a center of last years 
political activism were locked at 8 pm the public was barred from 
tiananmen square the center of the protests for the fourth day 
the few individuals who tried to protest the military crackdown 
were quickly arrested 
outside china people from mongolia to paris and czechoslovakia 
remembered the anniversary with hunger strikes marches and 
