originated many of the ideas 
the western plan includes a lowering of natos military profile 
as eastwest tensions subside and an acceleration of negotiations to 
ban shortrange nuclear weapons in both alliances 
also the officials said soviet troops could remain in what is 
now east german territory for some time the west germans would help 
