week photo district news other properties include marketing 
computers adbank and marketers guide to media 
the asm publications will become part of affiliateds specialty 
publishing and information subsidiary bpi communications inc bpi 
now publishes 15 specialty magazines 29 annual directories 
publishes and distributes specialty books under five imprints and 
operates two book clubs 
