<TEXT>
an industry committee of editors photo editors 
and production specialists will advise the associated press on the 
startup of its highspeed photo delivery and electronic darkroom 
systems 
they represent the departments or sections of a newspaper that 
will be most involved with the new photo technology said hal 
buell assistant to the president for photostream and the electronic 
darkrooms 
